    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/488470/extras/d94a8f805bc40dcc0f786313bd195e10.poster.avif?t=1731408710\" width=176 height=166 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/488470/extras/d94a8f805bc40dcc0f786313bd195e10.webm?t=1731408710\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/488470/extras/d94a8f805bc40dcc0f786313bd195e10.mp4?t=1731408710\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Shaman</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the wilderness with the Shaman. This elemental manipulator uses the forces of nature to his advantage and always has a tool for any situation. His skillset combines the talents of an elementalist with the chieftain’s mastery, binding his powers to totems that aid him in battle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Playstyle</strong>:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Shaman offers diverse playstyles, from continuously conjuring twisters and summoning meteor storms to taking a more passive approach by letting totems or spirit wolves do the fighting for him.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Recommended for:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players who enjoy a versatile caster capable of adapting to various scenarios.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Those who wish to conjure an army to fight on their behalf.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Anyone eager to master the elements.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Storm, Earth, and Fire, heed my call!</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
